Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.99,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:264610,266990}I don't like it.{NOTE:気に入らないねぇ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:28.62,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:266990,268620}Let's go, Storm!{NOTE:行くよストーム！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.97,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:282760,284970}Ah, Sand Barioth.{NOTE:あっ、ベリオロス座！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.97,0:04:49.85,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:284970,289850}The fact that we can see Sand Barioth means we're quite far to the South.{NOTE:ベリオロス座が見えるということはずいぶん南まで来ましたね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:54.23,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:289850,294230}Did you know that Sand Barioth is part of the "Love Premonition" constellation?{NOTE:知ってる？ベリオロス座の星座言葉は恋の予感｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:56.19,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:294230,296190}No, I didn't know that.{NOTE:そうなの？知らなかった｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:59.73,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:296190,299730}It's common knowledge for girls.\NThis month's lucky color is red.{NOTE:乙女の常識よ｡今月のラッキーカラーは赤｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.21,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:299730,301210}Red, huh?{NOTE:赤なんだ｡ん？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.53,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:304740,306530}Cheval, is something wrong?{NOTE:シュヴァルどうかした？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:07.70,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:306530,307700}It's nothing.{NOTE:いや｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.66,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:307700,310660}Just… Lute and I have always been together.{NOTE:俺とリュートはいつも一緒だった｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:14.21,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:311910,314210}The village was always at peace.{NOTE:村は平和だった｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.58,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:314210,315580}At least, until that day…{NOTE:あの日までは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.00,0:05:19.67,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:318000,319670}And then I sought power.{NOTE:俺は強さを求めた｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:24.59,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:320880,324590}Because I didn't want to let that tragedy happen ever again.{NOTE:もう二度とあんな悲劇を繰り返さないために｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:30.64,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:326630,330640}It blinded me into believing Manelger's words.{NOTE:そして、マネルガーの言葉に乗せられ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.31,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:330640,332310}And because of that…{NOTE:その結果…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.06,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:332310,335060}I drove the world to the brink of destruction.{NOTE:俺は世界を破滅の一歩手前まで追い込んだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.57,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:338310,341570}If it wasn't for Lute, I'd be…{NOTE:リュートがいなかったら俺は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.11,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:343150,344110}Oh?{NOTE:お？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:54.50,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:350120,354500}This time I have to work hard… for Lute's sake.{NOTE:だから今度は俺がリュートのために頑張らなきゃいけないんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.29,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:354500,358290}You're right. Let's do our best and save Avinia.{NOTE:そうだね｡頑張ってアユリアを捜しに行こう｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.17,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:358290,361170}– Now how about an Energy Drink!?\N– Ah…{NOTE:—よ～し、元気ドリンコ作ってあげる！\\N—あっ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.30,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:361170,362300}M-Maybe I'll…{NOTE:いやそれは…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.59,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:364090,366590}Here, my specially made Energy Drink!{NOTE:はい！特製元気ドリンコ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:08.51,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:366590,368510}T-Thanks.{NOTE:あ…ありがとう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.47,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:368510,370470}So that's an Energy Drink?{NOTE:これが元気ドリンコですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.85,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:370470,371850}You've never drank one?{NOTE:飲んだことないの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:16.52,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:371850,376520}Nope. I didn't know it had such sweet, tasty aroma.{NOTE:ええ｡こんなおいしそうな匂いがするなんて、思ってもいませんでした｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:18.77,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:376520,378770}I have to try it out.{NOTE:これはぜひとも頂かなければ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:22.82,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:379810,382820}Wait, it was meant for Cheval!{NOTE:あっ！それはシュヴァルのために…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.82,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:387450,388820}I-It's hot!{NOTE:あ…熱いです｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.07,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:388820,390070}It burns from the inside!{NOTE:燃えてきました｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.28,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:390070,391280}My coolness is melting!{NOTE:クールな私が…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.67,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:397330,399670}He became very energetic indeed.{NOTE:すっごく元気になってる｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:42.46,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:399670,402460}Lilia's Energy Drink lives up to its name.{NOTE:リリアの元気ドリンコは効くからね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.97,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:415260,416970}The weather's nice this morning!{NOTE:いい天気だね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.48,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:417520,419480}Alright, let's go.{NOTE:よし出発だ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:11.41,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:428030,431410}Today's my lucky day.\NSo many Kinship Stones.{NOTE:ありがたいねえ｡こんなたくさんの絆石を｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.24,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:432780,436240}Even if they're all worthless garbage.{NOTE:あんたたちと同じクズばかりだけどね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.58,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:440620,442580}Gildegaran is that way, right?{NOTE:こっちがギルデカランね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.71,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:442580,444710}I guess it's time for us to split up.{NOTE:ああ｡ここでお別れだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.25,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:444710,446250}Take care, Fifi.{NOTE:ティティもお元気で｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.25,0:07:27.46,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:446250,447460}You too, Cryo.{NOTE:クーリオもね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:37.31,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:454140,457310}They don't have any powerful Kinship Stones, right?{NOTE:力の強い絆石はないのかねえ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.31,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:501060,504310}It seems there's a bit of a wall between us.{NOTE:僕たち何か壁ありませんか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.98,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:508520,509980}I guess you're right.{NOTE:そうだね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.94,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:509980,511940}I can't really say there isn't one.{NOTE:壁がないとは言えないな｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.45,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:516820,518450}It's for the best.{NOTE:いいですね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:40.83,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:518450,520830}Let's keep this relationship cool.{NOTE:これからもクールな関係でいきましょう｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.42,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:529500,532420}Left or right?{NOTE:右か。左か｡\\N\\NJapanese read RTL so they say "right" first. It's more natural for Westerners to say "left" first.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:57.85,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:532420,537850}If I were to make a calm judgement, it's probably better not to go right.{NOTE:冷静に判断しますに…たぶん右の方がいいのではないでしょうか｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.26,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:537850,539260}Right, huh?{NOTE:右か｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:02.93,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:539260,542930}If it was Navirou, he'd probably choose left.{NOTE:これがナビルーだったら左に行くんだけど｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.27,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:542930,544270}So, let's go right.{NOTE:右にしようか｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.53,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:551730,554530}We should've turn left after all.{NOTE:やっぱり左だったかな｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:20.74,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:554530,560740}You're the ones who beat Riders around here\Nand take their Kinship Stones?{NOTE:貴様らじゃな｡近ごろここらのライダーを倒して、絆石を奪っとるやつらは｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:25.25,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:560740,565250}Eh? You know about the Ebon Riders, mister?{NOTE:えっ!?おじいさん、ブラックライダーズのこと知ってるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:26.37,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:565250,566370}Huh!?{NOTE:はあ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:30.92,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:566370,570920}{\fs50}You know about the Ebon Riders, mister?{NOTE:おじいさんはブラックライダーズのこと知ってるんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:33.21,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:570920,573210}Who are these Ebon Tigers!?{NOTE:誰がブラックタイガースじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:35.13,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:573210,575130}{NOTE:あっ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:38.22,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:575130,578220}He has a Kinship Stone, maybe he's a Rider?{NOTE:腕に絆石をはめてるから、ライダーみたいだけど｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:40.30,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:578220,580300}My ears can still hear you!{NOTE:まだまだ耳は聞こえるわい！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.97,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:581310,583970}We are not the Ebon Riders.{NOTE:俺たちはブラックライダーズじゃありません｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.68,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:583970,585680}But we are looking for them.{NOTE:あいつらを探しに…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.31,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:585680,588310}I'm not giving this Kinship Stone to anyone!{NOTE:この絆石は誰にも渡さんぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.40,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:588650,589400}Come!{NOTE:来い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.69,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:589400,591690}Ride On! Aptonoth!{NOTE:ライドオン！アプトノス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.12,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:597280,599120}She's my Aptonoth.{NOTE:わしのアプトノスじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:02.37,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:599120,602370}She can crush rocks with her Slipping Dive.{NOTE:スリッピングダイブは岩をも砕くぞ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:06.58,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:602370,606580}It's a waste to Ride On for guys like you.{NOTE:貴様らのような連中相手にライドオンするのももったいない｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.21,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:610790,613210}I will take you on myself.{NOTE:わしが直接成敗してやる｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:17.47,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:613920,617470}Tarba's fist: Velocidrome Stance!{NOTE:タルバ流ドスランポスの構え！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:20.22,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:619140,620220}Wow.{NOTE:すごい…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.47,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:620970,622470}So many openings.{NOTE:隙だらけですね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.60,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:626680,628600}Barioth Stance!{NOTE:ベリオロスの構えじゃ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:33.19,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:631310,633190}Next time right is for escapes only.{NOTE:次は右に逃げてください｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.86,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:633190,634860}Agreed.{NOTE:分かった｡右だね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.41,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:642320,643410}Ah, ow-ow-ow!{NOTE:痛たたた…}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:44.62,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:643410,644620}Mister!{NOTE:おじいさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.08,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:646370,648080}My own back surprised me.{NOTE:ぎっくり腰じゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:50.04,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:648080,650040}You can't win against time.{NOTE:年には勝てんのう｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.04,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:650040,652040}I wondered how it was going to end.{NOTE:どうなることかと思いました｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.92,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:652040,653920}I definitely didn't see {\i1}that{\i0} coming.{NOTE:ちょっと驚きました｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.42,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:653920,656420}You owe it to that blunder\Nthat I didn't kick your butts.{NOTE:不覚にもお前らに借りができたな｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:01.39,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:657260,661390}Did you not understand that we aren't the Ebon Riders?{NOTE:シｭヴｧルさんはブラｯクライダーズじゃないって、分かってもらえましたか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:03.35,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:661390,663350}Who are these Ebon Tigers?{NOTE:誰がブラックタイガースじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.89,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:664350,666890}Clearly you didn't.{NOTE:そこは聞き間違えるんですね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:11.06,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:666890,671060}We're looking for the Riders that snatch Kinship Stones.{NOTE:俺たちは絆石を奪っていくライダーを探してるんです｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.48,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:671060,672480}Hmm?{NOTE:ふ～ん…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:17.23,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:673690,677230}Young one, you have a sharp look.{NOTE:若いのいい目をしてるな｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:20.11,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:677230,680110}Alright, then. I'll take you on as my disciple!{NOTE:よし！わしの弟子にしてやろう｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.20,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:680110,681200}Eh!? What?{NOTE:えっ！そんな…}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:24.07,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:682070,684070}Nobody asked for your opinion.{NOTE:誰も頼んでませんけど｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:29.83,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:684070,689830}Don't hold back. As long as you stay with me,\Nyour skills will surely improve.{NOTE:遠慮するな｡わしのそばにいれば、お前らの腕も上達間違いなしじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.83,0:11:32.96,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:689830,692960}– We're—\N– Hahaha, no matter, no matter.{NOTE:—俺たちは…\\N—ハハハ｡構わん構わん｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:36.63,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:692960,696630}Besides, I can't walk without help now.{NOTE:そして今のわしは誰かおらんと歩けん｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.71,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:696630,698710}I guess it can't be helped.{NOTE:しかたありませんね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:45.22,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:703550,705220}Hey, folks!{NOTE:皆の衆！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:47.64,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:705220,707640}I brought a new disciple!{NOTE:新しい弟子を連れてきたぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.03,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:716690,719030}They don't look all that thrilled.{NOTE:歓迎されてないみたいだね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.15,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:719030,722150}Well, villagers do have a tendency to hate strangers.{NOTE:よそ者を嫌う村はたくさんありますから｡}
