Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.21,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:736420,738210}Mansion…?{NOTE:屋敷って…}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:24.47,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:743300,744470}Listen well.{NOTE:よいか｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.97,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:745430,746970}My disciples…{NOTE:弟子たるもの…}
