Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.93,Default,Villager C,0,0,0,,{TIME:785970,787930}Mr. Tarba must've been a bother to you.{NOTE:迷惑だったでしょタルバさんは｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.43,Default,Villager B,0,0,0,,{TIME:788720,791430}As you can see, he's a stubborn old man.{NOTE:ご覧のとおりの頑固じいさんでね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:15.23,Default,Villager B,0,0,0,,{TIME:791430,795230}He makes youngsters into his "disciples" and brings them here all the time.{NOTE:若いの見つけちゃあ弟子にしてやるって連れてくるんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:19.40,Default,Villager C,0,0,0,,{TIME:795230,799400}But at least we get to see new faces in the village quite often.{NOTE:でもそのおかげで村に新しい風が入ってくるじゃないの｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.94,Default,Villager B,0,0,0,,{TIME:799400,800940}That's just how it is.{NOTE:まあそうだね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:26.03,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:800940,806030}Even though grandpa Tarba\Nis a little crazy, our village needs him.{NOTE:タルバじいさんはあんなふうだけど、うちの村には必要な人なんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:30.20,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:806030,810200}Whenever a monster comes out of the forest,\Nhe drives them out with his Aptonoth.{NOTE:森にモンスターが出たときにはアプトノスで追っ払ってくれるんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.79,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:811160,813790}I have something to ask you.{NOTE:お聞きしたいことがあるんですが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:36.25,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:813790,816250}Have you ever heard of the Ebon Riders?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズってご存じですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:38.71,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:816250,818710}Who are those Ebon Tigers?{NOTE:誰がブラックタイガースじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.30,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:821090,823300}No, I can't say I have.{NOTE:いや～知らないね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:46.97,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:823300,826970}They rob Riders of their Kinship Stones.{NOTE:絆石を力ずくで奪っていく連中です｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.59,Default,Villager C,0,0,0,,{TIME:826970,828590}I've heard about that.{NOTE:聞いたことがある｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:52.47,Default,Villager C,0,0,0,,{TIME:828590,832470}The village to the south seems to have been hit hard.{NOTE:こっから南の村はずいぶん襲われたらしいわ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.93,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:832470,834930}Ebon Riders, hm?{NOTE:ブラックライダーズっていうのか｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:58.15,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:834930,838150}We need to be careful, right, Mr. Tarba?{NOTE:気を付けなきゃ｡なっ？タルバじいさん｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:01.23,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:838150,841230}Who are those Ebon Tigers!?{NOTE:誰がぶらっとタイガースじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.23,0:14:03.36,Default,Villager C,0,0,0,,{TIME:841230,843360}It's no use. He's completely drunk.{NOTE:駄目だ｡完全に酔ってる｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:07.49,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:844440,847490}Hey, aren't you from Hakum?{NOTE:お前さんたち、ハクム村の出なんじゃろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.37,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:847490,849370}How's Gamigami?{NOTE:ガミガミは元気か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.58,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:849370,851580}He's, um, doing fine.{NOTE:ええ｡元気ですけど｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:14.33,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:851580,854330}He and I are close friends.{NOTE:わしとあいつは親友なんじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.50,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:854330,855500}Eh?{NOTE:えっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:19.46,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:855500,859460}We used to compete a lot when we were younger.{NOTE:若いころあいつとは腕を競い合ったもんじゃよ｡\\N\\N腕を競う: arm wrestling?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:24.59,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:861500,864590}A younger Mr. Gamigami…?{NOTE:ガミガミさんの若いころ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:28.47,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:865920,868470}Grandpa, you just sit here and drink all you want.{NOTE:じいさんはおとなしくここで飲んでろ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.89,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:868470,870890}You know nothing about my younger days.{NOTE:わしの若いころを知らんな｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.85,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:870890,872850}Listen, you see… I…{NOTE:いいか、わしはなあ…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:37.06,Default,Villager B,0,0,0,,{TIME:872850,877060}You've traveled a long way. What brings you here?{NOTE:こんな所まで来るなんて、あなたたち何かあったの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:38.73,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:877730,878730}Well…{NOTE:実は…}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.16,Default,Villager B,0,0,0,,{TIME:890820,892160}I see.{NOTE:そう｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:54.20,Default,Villager B,0,0,0,,{TIME:892160,894200}You've had it rough.{NOTE:大変だったわね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:57.00,Default,Villager B,0,0,0,,{TIME:894200,897000}I hope you find your friend soon.{NOTE:お友達が早く見つかるといいわね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.89,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:910010,911890}It's the Ebon Riders!{NOTE:ブラックライダーズだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.43,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:911890,913430}Everyone, go back to your homes!{NOTE:みんな家に入れ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.43,Default,(unison),0,0,0,,{TIME:914350,915430}Somebody save us!{NOTE:助けてくれ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.60,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:917600,919600}Who do they think they are,\Nthose Ebon Tigers.{NOTE:何がブラックタイガースじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.40,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:919600,921400}As long as I'm still standing I…!{NOTE:このタルバがおるかぎり…}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:23.19,Default,Villager B,0,0,0,,{TIME:921400,923190}Mr. Tarba, it's no use!{NOTE:タルバじいさん、無理よ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:26.44,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:923190,926440}No use, you say? I protect this village!{NOTE:無理なもんか｡わしゃこの村を守るんじゃ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:27.73,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:926440,927730}Hey, disciple!{NOTE:おい弟子！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:33.16,Default,Old man,0,0,0,,{TIME:929450,933160}Protect the village in my place.{NOTE:わしの代わりに村を守ってくれ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.41,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:934450,935410}Understood.{NOTE:はい｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.41,0:15:36.91,Default,Villager A,0,0,0,,{TIME:935410,936910}Hey, are you sure about this?{NOTE:おい…大丈夫か？}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.37,0:15:40.08,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:938370,940080}I'll do what I can.{NOTE:やれるだけのことはやってみます｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.04,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:941000,943040}I'm Mr. Tarba's disciple after all.{NOTE:俺はタルバさんの弟子ですから｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.30,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:945960,947300}Ride On!{NOTE:ライドオン！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.67,0:15:50.63,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:949670,950630}Rathian!{NOTE:リオレイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.89,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:959890,961890}I don't like it.{NOTE:気に入らないねぇ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:04.73,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:961890,964730}To think they'd actually stand up against me.{NOTE:このあたしに立ち向かってくるなんて｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.06,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:964730,966060}Rathi!{NOTE:レイア！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.24,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:970990,972240}Where are they?{NOTE:どこだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:13.91,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:972240,973910}Cheval!{NOTE:シュヴァルさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.78,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:976660,977780}Running away?{NOTE:逃がすか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.79,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:979790,980790}There!{NOTE:いた！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:39.97,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:998970,999970}Cheval!{NOTE:シュヴァルさん！}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.57,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006900,1009570}Their Nargacuga is fast.{NOTE:向こうのナルガクルガはかなりのスピードだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.90,0:16:52.40,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010900,1012400}I can't catch up to them.{NOTE:あんなスピードあり得ない｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:22.68,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041770,1042680}Tsk!{NOTE:チッ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:24.10,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042680,1044100}A Sonic Bomb?{NOTE:音爆弾か｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.02,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044100,1045020}{NOTE:あっ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:34.24,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053070,1054240}Did they escape?{NOTE:逃がしたか｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.49,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059700,1061490}I don't like it.{NOTE:気に入らないねぇ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:44.75,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061490,1064750}To think that a mere boy could make me serious.{NOTE:あたしを本気にさせる坊やがいるなんて｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.67,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066960,1068670}Sync Ride!{NOTE:シンクライド！}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.09,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069790,1072090}It feels so good!{NOTE:気持ちＥ～！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:01.81,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080300,1081810}Impossible!{NOTE:そんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.31,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081810,1084310}A Nargacuga can't use lightning attacks!{NOTE:ナルガクルガに雷属性はないはず｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.52,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085810,1088520}That's the power of the Rite of Channeling!{NOTE:これが伝承の儀の力さ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:09.86,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088520,1089860}Lightning Breath!{NOTE:雷ブレス！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.91,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097610,1098910}What's wrong?{NOTE:どうしたんだい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.45,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098910,1101450}You're just running around in circles!{NOTE:ぐるぐる回ってるだけじゃないか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.70,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101450,1102700}It's no use.{NOTE:仕方ない｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.33,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102700,1105330}We'll switch to personal combat.{NOTE:一騎打ちだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:39.80,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118720,1119800}There!{NOTE:そこだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.23,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129600,1131230}I have to admit, boy.{NOTE:さすがだね坊や｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:56.03,Default,Shadow,1,1,0,,{TIME:1131230,1136030}Pretending to run aimlessly, spreading branches and leaves all over the place, and then standing in the center.{NOTE:ぐるぐる回っていると見せ掛けて、枝や葉を落として、その中心に立つ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:19:00.11,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136030,1140110}Getting close without making\Na sound is difficult, even for me.{NOTE:そりゃ音を立てずに近づくのはいくらあたしでも難しいよ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:01.11,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140110,1141110}Cheval…{NOTE:シュヴァルさん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.03,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141110,1143030}Don't worry about me.{NOTE:僕のことはいいですから｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.04,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143030,1145040}This is one noisy Felyne you've got.{NOTE:うるさいアイルーだね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:07.87,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145040,1147870}Aren't you the boy who wanted to become Redan?{NOTE:坊や、レダンになりたかったんだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.54,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148620,1150540}Who are you!?{NOTE:お前は何者だ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:11.92,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150540,1151920}Me?{NOTE:あたしかい？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:15.09,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151920,1155090}I'm one of the four Ebon Riders…{NOTE:あたしはブラックライダーズ四天王が一人…}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:16.05,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155090,1156050}Shadow.{NOTE:シャドウ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.76,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157920,1159760}Where's Avinia?{NOTE:アユリアはどこだ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.76,0:19:20.88,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159760,1160880}Avinia?{NOTE:アユリア？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.14,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160880,1164140}Ah, that little girl. She's doing fine.{NOTE:ああ、あの嬢ちゃん｡元気にしてるはずさ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:26.89,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164140,1166890}Unless that fool Wrath killed her off, that is.{NOTE:ラースのバカが殺してなきゃね｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:32.98,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168980,1172980}Now, how about you hand over that Kinship Stone of yours?{NOTE:さあ、その絆石こっちに渡してもらおうか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:34.86,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172980,1174860}What's your goal?{NOTE:何が目的なんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:36.94,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174860,1176940}Why are you collecting Kinship Stones?{NOTE:なぜ絆石を奪う！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:39.07,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176940,1179070}Deep inside, you understand us, don't you?{NOTE:坊やだったら分かるだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:41.41,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179070,1181410}We want to become stronger.{NOTE:強くなるためだよ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.37,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1183410,1185370}Strength by all means is justice.{NOTE:強さこそが正義｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.37,0:19:49.91,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185370,1189910}Weakness dies out, but the strongest always prevail.{NOTE:弱さは悪なんだよ｡弱いやつらは滅ぼしたっていいんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:51.79,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190790,1191790}You're wrong!{NOTE:違う！}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:56.29,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194040,1196290}Strength alone is worth nothing.{NOTE:強さだけじゃ駄目なんだ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.84,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196290,1197840}I know that the best.{NOTE:俺だから分かる｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.97,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197840,1199970}Strength isn't justice.{NOTE:強いことが正義じゃない｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.43,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199970,1202430}It's your virtues that makes you strong!{NOTE:正義だから強いんだ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.18,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202430,1204180}I don't like it.{NOTE:気に入らないねぇ｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.26,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204180,1206260}Why don't I just finish you off already?{NOTE:なぶり殺しにしてあげようか！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.10,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209220,1212100}Uh-oh. Just try taking another step.{NOTE:お～っと、一歩でも近づいてごらん｡}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.60,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212100,1214600}And see what happens to this Felyne here.{NOTE:このアイルーを…}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:29.29,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227620,1229290}Tail Crush!{NOTE:テイルクラッシュ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.13,0:20:36.92,Default,Cryo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235130,1236920}Impossible!{NOTE:そんなバカな｡}
